Task 3: Activity Notes
I utilized HackerRank to complete a beginner Python challenge, which reinforced my foundational coding skills in a structured, test-driven environment. 
For cloud collaboration, I built a 6-question Digital Literacy Awareness Quiz using Google Forms, linked directly to a Google Sheet for real-time response tracking. 
This exercise demonstrated how seamlessly Google Workspace handles data collection. 
Mastering these platforms is vital for my future AI group projects and technical interview preparations.
